        <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters135"/>
        <p>A <a href="ch77s13.html#PsionicMonsters134">folugub</a> can scent a crystal object up to 90 feet away, and once it has the scent, little deters it from its goal. It usually ceases attacking to devour a freshly liquefied crystal. The creature targets the largest crystal object available.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2478437"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters136"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Liquefy Crystal (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch77s13.html#PsionicMonsters134">folugub</a> that makes a successful touch attack with its tongue causes the target crystal to change phase, turning immediately from solid to liquid and becoming worthless. The touch can destroy up to a 5-foot cube of crystal instantly. Magic or psionic items made of crystal (including crystalline armor and weapons) must succeed on a DC 19 Reflex save or be liquefied. The save DC is Constitution-based and includes a +4 racial modifier.</p>
          <p>A crystalline weapon that deals damage to a <a href="ch77s13.html#PsionicMonsters134">folugub</a> becomes liquefied immediately.</p>
          <p/>
        </div>
